Preheat oven to 400 degrees F. Brown beef in large nonstick skillet; drain fat.* Add tomatoes and Recipe Ready Mirepoix and bring to a boil over high heat. Reduce heat to low and simmer 10 minutes. Stir in parsley and salt. Turn mixture into 1-1/2 quart casserole dish. Evenly top with mashed potatoes. Bake 20 minutes or until potatoes are golden and mixture is bubbling.